quran[28{c,v,t}:
74,48,uss waqt sifarish karne walon ki sifarish un ke kisi kaam nah aeye gi
74,49,aakhir inn logon ko kya ho gaya hai ke yeh iss nasiyaat se mun mourr rahay hain
74,50,goya yeh jungli gadhay hain
74,51,jo sher se dar kar bhaag parre hain
74,52,balkay inn mein se to har aik yeh chahta hai ke uss ke naam khulay khat beje jayen
74,53,"hargiz nahi, asal baat yeh hai ke yeh akhirat ka khauf nahi rakhtay"
74,54,"hargiz nahi, yeh to aik nasiyaat hai"
74,55,ab jis ka jee chahay is se sabaq haasil kar le
74,56,aur yeh koi sabaq haasil nah karen ge ila yeh ke Allah hi aisa chahay woh is ka haq daar hai ke uss se taqwa kya jaye aur woh is ka ahal hai ke ( taqwa karne walon ko ) bakhash day
75,1,"nahi, mein qasam khata hon qayamat ke din ki"
75,2,"aur nahi, mein qasam khata hon malamat karne walay nafs ki"
75,3,kya ensaan yeh samajh raha hai ke hum uss ki hadion ko jama nah kar saken ge ?
75,4,hum to is ki unglio ki poor poor taq theek bana dainay par Qadir hain
75,5,magar ensaan chahta yeh hai ke agay bhi bad a'maliyan karta rahay
75,6,"puchta hai"" aakhir kab aana hai woh qayamat ka din? """
75,7,phir jab daiday pathra jayen ge
75,8,aur chaand be noor ho jaayegaa
75,9,aur chaand Sooraj mila kar aik kar diye jayen ge
75,10,"uss waqt yahi ensaan kahe ga"" kahan bhaag kar jaoon? """
75,11,"hargiz nahi, wahan koi jaye panah nah hogi"
75,12,uss roz tairay Rab hi ke samnay ja kar tehrnahoga
75,13,uss roz ensaan ko is ka sab agla pichla kya karaya bta diya jaye ga
75,14,balkay ensaan khud hi apne aap ko khoob jaanta hai
75,15,chahay woh kitni hi mawzartain paish kere
75,16,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, iss wahi ko jaldi jaldi yaad karne ke liye apni zabaan ko harkat nah do"
75,17,iss ko yaad kara dena aur prhhwa dena hamaray zimma hai
75,18,lehaza jab hum isay parh rahay hon uss waqt tum iss ki qarat ko ghhor se suntay raho
75,19,phir is ka matlab samgha dena bhi hamaray zimma hai
